==Chinese==
===[[Mandarin]]===
[[Pinyin]]: bù yĭ chéngbài lùn yīngxióng

===Proverb===
'''[[不]][[以]][[成敗]][[論]][[英雄]]'''
# A person should not be deemed a hero merely on the basis of the success or failure of his endeavors.

===Alternate forms===
[[不以成败论英雄]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])

